The paper deals with wireless communication systems and optimization of spectral efficiency, which are topics covered in the Information Theory (cs.IT), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), and Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) sub-categories. The paper also discusses adaptive modulation and coding, which falls under the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the paper presents a nonlinear discrete optimization problem, which is a topic covered in the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category.
